OL,3,CAlmost #11 billion per year 'could be
OL,4,Cfreed up if people quit smoking'
OL,6,FIt will effectively raise the age of
OL,7,Ftobacco sales by one year every year,
OL,8,Fwith the aim of stopping today's
OL,9,Fyoungsters from ever taking up smoking
OL,10,Fin the first place.
OL,12,FIf the Bill passes, ministers say
OL,13,Fsmoking rates among those aged 14-30
OL,14,Fcould be near zero by 2040.
