OL,3,CAlmost #11 billion per year 'could be
OL,4,Cfreed up if people quit smoking'
OL,6,FThe new study, published in the
OL,7,Fjournal Tobacco Control and shared
OL,8,Fwith the PA news agency, included data
OL,9,Ffrom the Smoking Toolkit Study, made
OL,10,Fup of 18,721 smoking adults who
OL,11,Festimated how much they spent on
OL,12,Fsmoking.
OL,14,FThis was compared with figures from
OL,15,FGovernment tax receipts and national
OL,16,Festimates of illegal tobacco use.
