OL,4,Cfreed up if people quit smoking'
OL,6,FIt concluded: "The total dividend in
OL,7,FEngland is estimated to be #10.9
OL,8,Fbillion each year, which equates to
OL,9,F#1,776 per person who smokes or #246
OL,10,Fper adult regardless of smoking
OL,11,Fstatus."
